@startuml
actor "Manager" as MGR
boundary "UI Gaji" as UI
control "API /api/bwm/gaji" as API
database "Supabase\n(PostgreSQL)" as DB

== LIST GAJI ==
MGR -> UI: Buka /manager/bwm/gaji
UI -> API: GET /api/bwm/gaji
activate API
note right: Manager: tanpa teknisi_id -> semua data
API -> DB: SELECT gaji_teknisi + JOIN penugasan + JOIN profil
DB --> API: [{ teknisi, penugasan, periode, tunjangan, bonus, total, status }]
API --> UI: { data }
deactivate API
UI -> MGR: Tampil kartu summary + grup per penugasan

== REVIEW DETAIL ==
MGR -> UI: Klik header penugasan -> expand
UI -> MGR: Tampil daftar teknisi
MGR -> UI: Klik teknisi
UI -> API: (data sudah di cache, tidak perlu fetch ulang)
UI -> MGR: Dialog detail gaji

== UNDUH SLIP GAJI ==
MGR -> UI: Klik "Unduh Slip Gaji"
UI -> UI: import { downloadSlipGajiPdf } from '@/lib/pdf/payslip'
UI -> UI: downloadSlipGajiPdf(selectedGaji)
note right: generate PDF:\nmetadata hal 1,\nfoto before/after hal 2+
UI -> MGR: File PDF terunduh
@enduml
